desc_long							评测						“It’s a big, long, highly polished and incredibly challenging game, and for players looking for that sort of hardcore adventure experience”Gamezeebo												关于这款游戏							You lived through their side of the story—now live through his! Return once more to the haunted grounds of Ravenhearst Manor to uncover new details about this poignant saga. What you find could very well be the final chapter of this riveting story—if you escape.This is an intense psychological thriller that may reveal deep-seated fears. Not for the young or faint of heart.  Consider yourself warned.						
